snippet.title: Downtown theme from The Journey Down: Chapter Three
snippet.description:
"Downtown theme" aka "Soul of the City" from the Original Soundtrack of "The Journey Down: Chapter Three".
Composed by Jamie Salisbury.

"The Journey Down" is a point and click adventure game trilogy, with the third and final chapter launching september 21st 2017. Get it here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/579760/The_Journey_Down_Chapter_Three/

Sax: Simon Willescroft
Guitar: Jake Willson
Bass: Dave Marks
Drums: Accy Yeats
Mixed by Rich Aitken
